title: Chelone "Chilly" Miller
description:
Arbor Snowboards team rider, Chelone "Chilly" Miller believes the bigger the jump the better. We can't usually even find jumps big enough for him. At least there's Mammoth and June Mountain where he can count on kind of big jumps.
